      • printSummary

        public void printSummary(java.lang.String sTitle,
                         java.lang.String sElementName,
                         long nCount)
        Prints the given title, the total time since creation in seconds, and all measurements to System.out. If the number of elements processed is larger than 1 the time the processing of a single element took will be displayed too.
        Parameters:
        sTitle - The title string
        sElementName - The name of an element if nCount > 1
        nCount - The number of elements processed (must be >= 1)
